title: [Vornavian Coast, Forest Road]
description: A magnificent garden, expertly tended, fills the entire area.  Tomatoes, cucumbers, lettuce, carrots, and vegetables of all sorts grow in neatly tended rows here.  Fireflies hover over the variety of plant life, tiny torches blinking in the night.

A magnificent garden, expertly tended, fills the entire area.  Tomatoes, cucumbers, lettuce, carrots, and vegetables of all sorts grow in neatly tended rows here.  Bees buzz from row to row, taking advantage of the bounty and variety of plant life.
